=== 外交 ===
{{Main|克羅地亞外交}}
[[File:Svecanost_podizanja_NATOve_zastave_Zagreb_77.jpg|thumb]]]]
克罗地亚现已與183個國家建立了外交關係<ref name="tportal-DiplRel">{{hr}}{{cite web
|publisher=t-portal
|url=http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/svijet/126015/Vatikan-nije-medu-prvima-priznao-Hrvatsku.html
|title=S kojim državama nemamo diplomatske odnose?
|author=Drago Pilsel
|date=2011-05-05
|accessdate=2016-07-03
|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502024207/http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/svijet/126015/Vatikan-nije-medu-prvima-priznao-Hrvatsku.html
|archivedate=2016-05-02
|deadurl=no
}}</ref>(参见[[克罗地亚建交列表|克罗地亚建交列表]])。截至2019年，克國在海外共設有61個大使館、26個領事館和9個常駐外交使團，國內也駐有56個外國駐使館、70個領事館和多個海外國際組織辦事處，包括「[[欧洲重建和发展银行|欧洲重建和发展银行]]」、「[[國際移民組織|國際移民組織]]」、「歐洲安全與合作組織」、「[[世界銀行集團|世界銀行集團]]」、「[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]」、「[[前南斯拉夫问题国际刑事法庭|前南斯拉夫问题国际刑事法庭]]」、「[[联合国开发计划署|联合国开发计划署]]」、「[[联合国难民署|联合国难民署]]」與「[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]」等等<ref name="MVP-foreign-missions">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Ministarstvo vanjskih i europskih poslova
 | url = http://www.mvep.hr/en/diplomatic-directory/diplomatic-missions-and-consular-offices-to-croatia/
 | title = MVEP • Diplomatic Missions and Consular Offices to Croatia
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160706084509/http://www.mvep.hr/en/diplomatic-directory/diplomatic-missions-and-consular-offices-to-croatia/
 | archivedate = 2016-07-06
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。克國外交政策目標為加強與鄰國的關係、發展國際合作、促進克國經濟發展與樹立起現代化的民主歐洲國家之形象<ref name="MVPEI-Goals">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Ministarstvo vanjskih i europskih poslova
 | url = http://un.mfa.hr/?mh=151&mv=840
 | title = Foreign Policy Aims
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120127073846/http://un.mfa.hr/?mh=151&mv=840
 | archivedate = 2012-01-27
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref><ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|314}}。

自2003年起，加入[[歐盟|歐盟]]一直是克國外交首要的戰略目標<ref name="EU-NATO-StrategicGoals-NCL">{{hr}}{{cite web
 |publisher   = Nacional (weekly)
 |url         = http://www.nacional.hr/clanak/21036/mesiceva-podrska-un-u-blokira-ulazak-hrvatske-u-nato
 |title       = Mesićeva podrška UN-u blokira ulazak Hrvatske u NATO
 |date        = 2005-10-17
 |author      = Eduard Šoštarić
 |accessdate  = 2011-09-24
 |archivedate = 2012-06-30
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/68ocR483H?url=http://www.nacional.hr/clanak/21036/mesiceva-podrska-un-u-blokira-ulazak-hrvatske-u-nato
}}</ref><ref name="Sabor-EU-NATO-Strategic">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Sabor
 | url = http://www.sabor.hr/Default.aspx?art=1680
 | title = Izvješća o aktivnostima saborskih dužnosnika – rujan 2005: Odbor za parlamentarnu suradnju i odnose s javnošću Skupštine Zapadnoeuropske unije posjetio Hrvatski sabor
 | date = 2005-09-26
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archivedate = 2012-01-18
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120118190958/http://www.sabor.hr/Default.aspx?art=1680
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。2011年12月，克羅地亞完成了與歐盟的談判，於同年12月9日簽署了{{link-en|2011年加入協議|Treaty of Accession 2011|入盟協議}}<ref name="EU-Negotiations-Completed">{{en}}{{cite web 
 |url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=IP/11/824&format=HTML&aged=0&language=EN&guiLanguage=en 
 |title=EU closes accession negotiations with Croatia 
 |date=2011-06-30 
 |publisher=European Commission 
 |accessdate=2016-07-06 
 |archivedate=2011-07-08 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708034141/http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=IP%2F11%2F824&format=HTML&aged=0&language=EN&guiLanguage=en 
 |deadurl=yes 
 }}</ref><ref name="EU-Accession-Treaty">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = EU Newsroom
 | url = http://europa.eu/news/external-relations/2011/03/20110302_en.htm
 | title = Croatia signs EU accession treaty
 | date = 2011-12-09
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archivedate = 2011-12-08
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111208114657/http://europa.eu/news/external-relations/2011/03/20110302_en.htm
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。標誌著克國自2001年簽署《{{link-en|穩定與聯合進程|Stabilisation and Association Process|穩定與聯合協議}}》、2003年正式申請加入歐盟的努力得到了結果<ref name="NYTimes-Croatia-EU-2013">{{en}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = The New York Times
 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/11/world/europe/11iht-croatia11.html
 | title = Croatia Given Conditional Approval to Join E.U. in 2013
 | date = 2011-06-10
 | author = Stephen Castle
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160706130349/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/11/world/europe/11iht-croatia11.html
 | archivedate = 2016-07-06
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。克國入盟的主要障礙為{{link-en|克羅地亞—斯洛維尼亞邊界問題|Croatia–Slovenia border disputes|與鄰國斯洛維尼亞的邊界問題}}和就「[[前南斯拉夫問題國際刑事法庭|前南斯拉夫問題國際刑事法庭]]」的戰犯引渡合作爭議<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 | publisher = BBC News
 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4337777.stm
 | title = EU stalls over talks with Croatia
 | date = 2005-03-10
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160706130817/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4337777.stm
 | archivedate = 2016-07-06
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|publisher=BBC News|title=Slovenia unblocks Croatian EU bid|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8250441.stm|date=2009-09-11|accessdate=2016-07-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706131035/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8250441.stm|archivedate=2016-07-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>，前者於2009年11月4日透過斯國人公投和其議會決定，簽署協議而獲得解決<ref name="NYTimes-Croatia-Slovenia-Arbitration">{{en}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = The New York Times
 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/07/world/europe/07iht-slovenia.html
 | title = Slovenians Seem to Favor Arbitration in Border Dispute With Croatia
 | date = 2010-06-06
 | agency = [[路透社|路透社]]
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100610090134/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/07/world/europe/07iht-slovenia.html
 | archivedate = 2010-06-10
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。後者的情況則是海牙國際法庭起訴多名在南斯拉夫內戰中犯下戰爭罪行、種族清洗的克國將軍，但這些人卻在國內被視為[[民族英雄|民族英雄]]，因此引起很大的爭議。經過雙方長期的談判後，海牙法庭最終僅提出五位戰犯，其中三人已自首、一人去世。2005年12月，最後一位戰犯[[安特·戈托維納|安特·戈托維納]]也於[[西班牙|西班牙]]被捕，進而獲得極大的進展<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|325-326}}。2013年7月1日，克羅地亞正式加入歐盟，成為其第28個成員國<ref name="NYTimes-Croatia-EU-2013"/>。

克羅地亞另一個外交戰略目標為加入[[北大西洋公約組織|北大西洋公約組織]]<ref name="EU-NATO-StrategicGoals-NCL"/><ref name="Sabor-EU-NATO-Strategic"/>；2000年，北約的「{{link-en|和平夥伴關係|Partnership for Peace}}」計劃將克國涵蓋了進去，2008年時更邀請該國加入北約，2009年4月1日，克羅地亞正式加入北約<ref name="NYTimes-Bush-Zagreb">{{en}}{{cite news|newspaper=The New York Times|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/05/world/europe/05cnd-prexy.html|title=Bush Champions Expansive Mission for NATO|date=2008-04-05|author=Steven Lee Myers|accessdate=2016-07-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115024457/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/05/world/europe/05cnd-prexy.html|archivedate=2012-11-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="BBC-Croatia-NATO">{{en}}{{cite news
 | publisher = BBC News
 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/7977332.stm
 | title = Nato welcomes Albania and Croatia
 | date = 2009-04-01
 | accessdate = 2016-07-06
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120417221006/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/7977332.stm
 | archivedate = 2012-04-17
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。克國未來還打算加入[[申根區|申根區]]<ref>{{hr}}{{cite news
|url=http://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/karamarko-granicni-nadzor-prema-eu-ukidamo-2015-clanak-248519
|title=Karamarko: Granični nadzor prema EU ukidamo 2015.
|author=Stojan de Prato
|date=2011-02-04
|newspaper=Večernji list
|accessdate=2016-07-06
|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104050846/http://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/karamarko-granicni-nadzor-prema-eu-ukidamo-2015-clanak-248519
|archivedate=2011-11-04
|deadurl=no
}}</ref>，但[[歐洲移民危機|歐洲移民危機]]成了其最大的障礙<ref name=hungarycroatia>{{en}}{{cite web
|url=http://news.yahoo.com/hungary-could-block-croatias-schengen-accession-aide-pm-105034474.html
|title=Hungary could block Croatia's Schengen accession: aide to PM
