 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。克國流量最大的高速公路是{{link-en|國道A1號 (克羅地亞)|A1 (Croatia)|國道A1號}}，這條路連結了萨格勒布到斯普利特和橫貫斯拉沃尼亞與克羅地亞西北部的{{link-en|國道A3號 (克羅地亞)|A3 (Croatia)|國道A3號}}<ref name="HC-promet">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Hrvatske ceste
 | url = http://www.hrvatske-ceste.hr/WEB%20-%20Legislativa/brojenje-prometa/CroDig2009.pdf
 | title = Traffic counting on the roadways of Croatia in 2009 – digest
 | format = PDF
 | archivedate = 2011-07-21
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721100545/http://www.hrvatske-ceste.hr/WEB%20-%20Legislativa/brojenje-prometa/CroDig2009.pdf
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。克國境內的國道交通網路連結了全部的主要人口居住地，其高速公路高品質和高安全性，並通過了「歐洲隧道評估計劃」（European Tunnel Assessment
Program）和「歐洲測試」（EuroTest）的要求<ref>{{en}}{{cite web
 | url = http://www.eurotestmobility.com/news.php?item=25&PHPSESSID=a7d9b4decd981bb3cdc3494656b0104d
 | title = EuroTest
 | publisher = Eurotestmobility.com
 | archivedate = 2011-04-30
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110430010646/http://www.eurotestmobility.com/news.php?item=25&PHPSESSID=a7d9b4decd981bb3cdc3494656b0104d
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。

克羅地亞有著廣泛的鐵路網，截至2014年，其鐵路總長為{{convert|2604|km|abbr=off}}，其中{{convert|970|km|abbr=off}}電氣化、{{convert|254|km|abbr=off}}為雙軌鐵路<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|370}}，最重要的鐵路是分別通過「泛歐走廊」的「第五B號」（里耶卡至布達佩斯）和「第十號」（盧比安納至貝爾格勒）這兩條，而且它們都有經過首都萨格勒布<ref name="Helsinki-1997"/>{{rp|49-65}}。克國的所有鐵路皆由國營企業——「[[克罗地亚铁路|克罗地亚铁路]]」營運<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 | website = Europe railway
 | title = Trains in Croatia
 | url = http://www.interrail.eu/trains-europe/trains-country/trains-croatia
 | archivedate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160703103913/http://www.interrail.eu/trains-europe/trains-country/trains-croatia
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。

克國共有[[萨格勒布机场|萨格勒布]]、[[扎達爾機場|扎達爾]]、{{link-en|史普利特機場|Split Airport|史普利特}}、[[杜布罗夫尼克机场|杜布罗夫尼克]]、[[里耶卡機場|里耶卡]]、[[奧西耶克機場|奧西耶克]]和[[普拉機場|普拉]]等七處[[国际机场|国际机场]]<ref name="MMPI-Airports">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Ministry of the Sea, Transport and Infrastructure
 | title = Air transport
 | url = http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=675
 | archivedate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160703104330/http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=675
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。

克羅地亞最繁忙的貨運[[港口|港口]]是[[里耶卡港|里耶卡港]]，客運港口則為{{link-en|斯普利特港|Port of Split}}和扎達爾港<ref name="WB-Rijeka">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher=World Bank
 | title=Riječka luka –jadranski "prolaz" prema Europi
 | date=2006-03-03
 | accessdate=2011-10-13
 | url=http://go.worldbank.org/V9N60RX7L0
 | archive-date=2012-08-05
 | archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20120805200119/http://go.worldbank.org/V9N60RX7L0
 | dead-url=yes
 }}</ref><ref name="MMPI-RL-plan">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher=Ministry of the Sea, Transport and Infrastructure (Croatia)
 | url=http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=480
 | title=Luke
 | accessdate=2011-08-24
 | archive-date=2012-12-16
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121216063733/http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=480
 | dead-url=yes
 }}</ref>，另外還有定期渡輪航線與意大利沿海城市相連結，眾多的小型港口也以此連結著克國的島嶼與沿海城市<ref name="AOLPP-Rijeka">{{hr}}{{cite web
 |publisher   = Agencija za obalni linijski pomorski promet
 |url         = http://www.agencija-zolpp.hr/Brodskelinije/tabid/1267/Default.aspx
 |title       = Plovidbeni red za 2011. godinu
 |archivedate = 2011-07-15
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20110715203314/http://www.agencija-zolpp.hr/Brodskelinije/tabid/1267/Default.aspx
 |accessdate  = 2016-07-12
 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref>。克國最大的內河港口為多瑙河畔的武科瓦爾，為該國通往「泛歐走廊」第7區的出口<ref name="Helsinki-1997"/>{{rp|49-65}}<ref name="MMPI-River-Navigation">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Ministry of the Sea, Transport and Infrastructure (Croatia)|url=http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=890|title=Plovni putovi|trans_title=Navigable routes|accessdate=2011-09-10|archive-date=2012-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121216060844/http://www.mppi.hr/default.aspx?id=890|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

克國國內有長達{{convert|610|km|abbr=off}}的[[输油管道|输油管道]]，連結著里耶卡港的油庫一直到里耶卡和錫薩克的煉油廠和數個轉運碼頭，該系統每年運輸量約有2000萬噸<ref name="JANAF-system">{{en}}{{cite web|publisher=Jadranski naftovod|url=http://www.janaf.hr/index.php?option=sustav&lang=en|title=The JANAF system|accessdate=2011-10-08|archive-date=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331045338/http://www.janaf.hr/index.php?option=sustav&lang=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。天然氣運輸系統則有{{convert|2113|km|abbr=off}}長，分為主管線和區管線，並有超過300個相關設施連接著鑽井台、{{link-hr|奧可里|Okoli}}當地的天然氣儲存庫、27個終端用戶和37座分發系統<ref name="Plinacro-system">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Plinacro|url=http://www.plinacro.hr/default.aspx?id=264|title=Transportni sustav|accessdate=2011-10-08|archive-date=2012-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120127131605/http://www.plinacro.hr/default.aspx?id=264|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2013年時，克國的初級能源生產結構中天然氣佔了38.2％、原油佔了12.4％、木材燃料14.3％、水力30.5％<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|325}}。2014年時，克國的總電力產量達到13,082千兆瓦，另外還有約28.5％來自進口<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|322}}。克國進口的電能主要來自於斯洛維尼亞的[[克爾什科核電廠|克爾什科核電廠]]，克國國有企業「{{link-en|克羅地亞電力公司|Hrvatska elektroprivreda}}」擁有該核電廠50％的經營權，該廠約供應了克國15％的電力<ref name="EUB-NEK">{{en}}{{cite web|publisher=EU Business|url=http://www.eubusiness.com/news-eu/japan-disaster.9bc|title=Croatia, Slovenia's nuclear plant safe: Croatian president|date=2011-03-28|accessdate=2011-10-08|archive-date=2011-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923171546/http://www.eubusiness.com/news-eu/japan-disaster.9bc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
{{-}}

==社會==
===族群與信仰===
{{main|克羅地亞宗教}}
[[File:Croatian_censuses_1857-2011.gif|thumb]]
截至2014年12月31日，克羅地亞共有4,225,316人口<ref name="人口統計2014">{{en}}{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Bureau of Statistics|url=http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/system/first_results.htm#MIG|title=The Policy of Immigration in Croatia|accessdate=2016-06-09|archive-date=2017-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705025245/http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/system/first_results.htm#MIG|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[国家人口密度列表|人口密度]]為每平方公里75人，2012年時國人[[各国人口预期寿命列表|預期壽命]]為78歲<ref name=who0>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://gamapserver.who.int/gho/interactive_charts/mbd/life_expectancy/atlas.html|title=WHO Life Expectancy at birth|accessdate=2014-12-06|publisher=World Health Organization|year=2012|archive-date=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206093205/http://gamapserver.who.int/gho/interactive_charts/mbd/life_expectancy/atlas.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，2014年的[[总和生育率|总和生育率]]則為每位母親扶養1.46名子女，為[[各国生育率列表|世界上最低的一個國家]]<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|122}}。根據目前的出生率與移民比率，克羅地亞中央統計局估計克國人口將在2051年時降至310萬人<ref name="DZS-Forecast-2051">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Croatian Bureau of Statistics|format=PDF|url=http://www.dzs.hr/Hrv/important/Notices/projekcije_stanovnistva_2004-2051.pdf|title=Projekcija stanovništva Republike Hrvatske 2004. – 2051.|year=2006|accessdate=2011-10-11|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619230054/http://www.dzs.hr/Hrv/important/Notices/projekcije_stanovnistva_2004-2051.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。克國自1857年第一次人口普查的218.2萬人穩定上升到1991年的最高峰——478.4萬人<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|18}}。克國在1970年代完成了人口轉換，至今國家人口已呈現負成長<ref>{{hr}}{{cite journal|author1=Snježana Mrđen|author2=Mladen Friganović|date=1998-06|title=The demographic situation in Croatia|journal=Geoadria|publisher=Hrvatsko geografsko društvo – Zadar|issn=1331-2294|volume=3|issue=1|url=http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=14991|access-date=2016-07-11|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217034934/https://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=14991|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|29-56}}，因此近幾年來克國政府倍感壓力，逐年增加40％的外籍勞工配額<ref>{{hr}}{{cite web|url=http://www.poslovni.hr/vijesti/trazi-se-40-vise-kvota-za-strane-radnike-101937.aspx|title=Traži se 40% više kvota za strane radnike|publisher=Poslovni dnevnik|date=2008-11-28|accessdate=2010-05-16|archive-date=2012-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120418231417/http://www.poslovni.hr/vijesti/trazi-se-40-vise-kvota-za-strane-radnike-101937.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時也試著推出移民政策，試圖吸引移出者回國<ref>{{hr}}{{cite journal|journal=Politička misao: Croatian Political Science Review|issn=0032-3241|volume=35|issue=5|year=2008|url=http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=51084|title=The Policy of Immigration in Croatia|author=Nick Vidak|publisher=University of Zagreb, Faculty of Political Science|accessdate=2010-10-15|archive-date=2020-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206140644/https://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=51084|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|57-75}}。

克國人口減少的原因主要有四：首先是歷經獨立戰爭和世界大戰的戰後嬰兒潮，造成出生率上升，隨後即急遽下降；二是人口預期壽命的延長；三為大量青年移民國外<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|19}}；四則是獨立戰爭造成大量的平民流離失所、遠走他鄉。1991年時，在克國境內的塞爾維亞人居住地區裡，超過40萬的克羅地亞與非塞爾維亞人為逃脫塞人的暴力威脅而被迫遷移<ref>{{hr}}{{cite web |url=http://www.un.org/icty/pressreal/2007/pr1162e-summary.htm |title=Summary of judgement for Milan Martić |date=2007-06-12 |publisher=United Nations |accessdate=2008-06-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215084458/http://www.un.org/icty/pressreal/2007/pr1162e-summary.htm |archivedate=2007-12-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。1995年，獨立戰爭最後幾天時，超過12萬的克籍塞爾維亞人（另一說為20萬<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|author=Matt Prodger|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/4747379.stm|title=Evicted Serbs remember Storm|publisher=BBC News|date=2005-08-05|accessdate=2011-10-15|archive-date=2009-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090219223101/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/4747379.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>）在克軍發動「暴風行動」抵達前逃離了國家<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2000/01/16/world/for-serbs-in-croatia-a-pledge-unkept.html|title=For Serbs in Croatia, a Pledge Unkept|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2011-10-15|author=Steven Erlanger|date=2000-01-16|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503052051/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/01/16/world/for-serbs-in-croatia-a-pledge-unkept.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。戰爭結束後十年期間，總計超過30萬的克籍塞爾維亞難民也僅有約117,000人返回克國<ref name="OSCE-Reform"/>。據估計，總共約有200萬克羅埃西亞人生活在其他國家<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|21}}。

克國民族構成略為複雜，根據2011年克國中央統計局的資料，全國人口有90.4％為[[克羅地亞人|克羅地亞人]]<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|116}}，是前南斯拉夫各共和國中民族最為單一的，但少數民族多樣，包括塞爾維亞人（4.4％）和共佔剩餘5.2％的[[波士尼亞人|波士尼亞人]]、[[匈牙利人|匈牙利人]]、[[意大利人|意大利人]]、[[斯洛維尼亞人|斯洛維尼亞人]]、[[德國人|德國人]]、[[捷克人|捷克人]]、羅馬尼亞人和阿爾巴尼亞人等不同民族<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|116}}。目前仍定居於克羅地亞的大部分塞爾維亞人都從未居住在獨立戰爭中塞族軍隊的佔領區，而戰爭結束後回歸的塞族人也只有部份重新安置於故居，其他部份地區則被配發給從波黑的[[塞族共和國|塞族共和國]]逃出來得克羅地亞難民<ref name="Index-Cro-Refugees">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Index.hr|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/savez-udruga-hrvataiz-bih-izabrao-novo-celnistvo/145769.aspx|title=Savez udruga Hrvata iz BiH izabrao novo čelništvo|date=2003-06-28|accessdate=2011-10-12|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155846/http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/savez-udruga-hrvataiz-bih-izabrao-novo-celnistvo/145769.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PresidentRH-refugees">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Office of the President of Croatia|url=http://www.predsjednik.hr/29062010|title=29 06 2010 – Benkovac|date=2010-06-29|accessdate=2011-10-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121124095611/http://www.predsjednik.hr/29062010|archivedate=2012-11-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

克羅地亞人主要信仰[[天主教會|羅馬天主教]]，比率約86.3％，其他宗派還有4.4％的[[東正教|東正教]]、0.6％其他派別的[[基督宗教|基督宗教]]、1.5％[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]和0.4％其他宗教信仰者，以及有6.7％的人為[[無神論|無神論]]或[[不可知论|不可知论]]者<ref name="Census2011-religion">{{hr}}{{cite web|url=http://www.dzs.hr/Hrv/censuses/census2011/results/htm/usp_04_HR.htm|title=STANOVNIŠTVO PREMA VJERI, POPISI 2001. I 2011.|publisher=Croatian Bureau of Statistics|year=2013|accessdate=2013-05-12|archive-date=2017-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610082808/http://www.dzs.hr/Hrv/censuses/census2011/results/htm/usp_04_HR.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
{{克羅地亞最大城市}}
{{-}}

===語言===
克國的官方語言為[[克羅地亞語|克羅地亞語]]，在加入歐盟後也跟著成為該組織的第24種官方語言<ref name="Ustav-RH">{{hr}}{{cite news|newspaper=Narodne Novine|url=http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2010_07_85_2422.html|title=Ustav Republike Hrvatske|date=2010-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429184812/http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2010_07_85_2422.html|archivedate=2016-04-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="VL-Hrvatski-EU">{{hr}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = Večernji list
 | url = http://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/hrvatski-postaje-24-sluzbeni-jezik-europske-unije-clanak-211879
 | title = Hrvatski postaje 24. službeni jezik Europske unije
 | date = 2011-11-05
 | author1 = Sandra Veljković
 | author2 = Stojan de Prato
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130827100338/http://www.vecernji.hr/vijesti/hrvatski-postaje-24-sluzbeni-jezik-europske-unije-clanak-211879
 | archivedate = 2013-08-27
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。克國法律也有規定少數民族可在特定條件下使用[[捷克語|捷克語]]、[[匈牙利語|匈牙利語]]、[[意大利語|意大利語]]、[[魯塞尼亞語|魯塞尼亞語]]、[[塞爾維亞語|塞爾維亞語]]和[[斯洛伐克語|斯洛伐克語]]這些少數民族的語言<ref>{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Sabor|url=http://www.sabor.hr/Default.aspx?art=23872|title=Izviješće o provođenju ustavnog zakona o pravima nacionalnih manjina i utrošku sredstava osiguranih u državnom proračunu Republike Hrvatske za 2007. godinu za potrebe nacionalnih manjina|date=2008-11-28|accessdate=2016-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712145251/http://www.sabor.hr/Default.aspx?art=23872|archivedate=2016-07-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

1961至1991年期間，克羅地亞的官方語言是[[塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语|塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语]]。在共產黨政府統治期間，克國人總將自己的語言定名為「克羅地亞-塞爾維亞語」，而不是「塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语」或「克羅地亞語」<ref>{{hr}}{{cite journal
 | journal = Kolo
 | publisher = Matica hrvatska
 | issn = 1331-0992
 | year = 2009
 | issue = 1-2
 | url = http://www.matica.hr/kolo/kolo2009_1.nsf/AllWebDocs/Polozaj_hrvatskoga_jezika_u_svijetu_danas
 | title = Položaj hrvatskoga jezika u svijetu danas
 | author = Mate Kapović
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112075048/http://www.matica.hr/kolo/kolo2009_1.nsf/AllWebDocs/Polozaj_hrvatskoga_jezika_u_svijetu_danas
 | archivedate = 2012-01-12
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。克羅地亞語和塞爾維亞語的差異長時間一直是爭議焦點，當時南斯拉夫官方並不承認這兩種是不同的語言，而是視為東西兩方、使用[[拉丁字母|拉丁字母]]和[[塞尔维亚语西里尔字母|塞尔维亚语西里尔字母]]的同一種語言<ref name="Brozović-HRV"/>。具有標誌性的一次事件是1967年克羅地亞、塞爾維亞和黑山的文化部達成協議出版了一部權威性的塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语辭典時引爆克國知識界的極大不滿，後者聲稱這部著作中將許多常見的克羅地亞字彙不是排斥，就是被當作方言處理，連發音都以塞爾維亞讀音為正宗，引起了克羅地亞人的文化危機意識，批評此為塞爾維亞沙文主義的表現、企圖抹殺克羅地亞的民族性<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|26-27}}。

根據2011年的統計報告，95.6％的克羅地亞人以克羅地亞語為母語、1.2％為塞爾維亞語，其餘的各種語言使用者則都不超過克羅地亞總人口的0.5％<ref name="Census-2011">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Croatian Bureau of Statistics
 | title = 5. POPULATION BY MOTHER TONGUE, BY TOWNS/MUNICIPALITIES, 2011 CENSUS
 | url = http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/census2011/results/htm/e01_01_08/e01_01_08_RH.html
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712145733/http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/census2011/results/htm/e01_01_08/e01_01_08_RH.html
 | archivedate = 2016-07-12
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。克羅地亞語是[[南斯拉夫语支|南斯拉夫語系]]的一支，大部分的克語詞彙自印歐語族斯拉夫分支所衍生而成，書寫使用的是[[拉丁字母|拉丁字母]]，有三種主要方言：「[[舒特方言|舒特]]」、「[[卡伊方言|卡伊]]」和「[[查方言|查]]」。「舒特」使用範圍較廣，與標準克語相似，而「卡伊」和「查」的差別在於詞彙、[[音位學|音位學]]和[[语法学|语法学]]的不同<ref name="Brozović-HRV">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Institute of Croatian Language and Linguistics
 | title = Organska podloga hrvatskog jezika
 | url = http://www.ihjj.hr/oHrJeziku-povijest-1.html
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110807082335/http://www.ihjj.hr/oHrJeziku-povijest-1.html
 | archivedate = 2011-08-07
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。根據2009年的調查，有78％的克羅地亞人聲稱至少會一種外語<ref name="Index-lang">{{hr}}{{cite web|publisher=Index.hr|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/istrazivanje-tri-posto-visokoobrazovanih-ne-zna-niti-jedan-strani-jezik-hrvati-uglavnom-znaju-engleski/545687.aspx|title=Istraživanje: Tri posto visokoobrazovanih ne zna niti jedan strani jezik, Hrvati uglavnom znaju engleski|date=2011-04-05|accessdate=2016-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110406204635/http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/istrazivanje-tri-posto-visokoobrazovanih-ne-zna-niti-jedan-strani-jezik-hrvati-uglavnom-znaju-engleski/545687.aspx|archivedate=2011-04-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>，而[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧洲联盟委员会]]2005年報告指出，有49％的克國人選擇[[英语|英语]]作為第二語言、34％為[[德语|德语]]和14%的[[意大利语|意大利语]]<ref name="EBS-243">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_243_en.pdf|date=2006-02|title=Europeans and their languages – European commission special barometer FEB2006|publisher=European Commission|format=PDF|accessdate=2016-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414102658/http://ec.europa.eu/public_opinion/archives/ebs/ebs_243_en.pdf|archivedate=2016-04-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

===教育體制===
[[File:University_of_Zagreb.jpg|220px]]是克羅地亞最大的大學]]
克羅地亞國民識字率達99.2％<ref>{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Croatian Bureau of Statistics
 | url = http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/census2011/results/htm/e01_01_33/E01_01_33.html
 | title = Population aged 10 and over by sex and illiterates by age, 2011 census
 | accessdate = 2015-12-26
 | archivedate = 2016-06-29
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160629133830/http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/census2011/results/htm/e01_01_33/E01_01_33.html
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。根據2010年8月出版的《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》就不同國家生活品質所作的一份世界調查，將克國的教育系統排名為世界第22名，與奧地利同位<ref name="Newsweek-ranking">{{en}}{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.newsweek.com/2010/08/15/interactive-infographic-of-the-worlds-best-countries.html
 |title       = Newsweek study of Health, Education, Economy and Politics ranks the globe's top nations
 |publisher   = [[新闻周刊|Newsweek]]
 |date        = 2010-08-15
 |accessdate  = 2010-11-14
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/5sQWPP1Ay?url=http://www.newsweek.com/2010/08/15/interactive-infographic-of-the-worlds-best-countries.html
 |archivedate = 2010-09-01
 |deadurl     = no
}}</ref>。克國的小學教育自六、七歲開始，分成八個學級，2007年時又通過一項法律，增加免費的、非義務性的教育到18歲為止。中學教育則提供「[[文理中学|文理中学]]」和「[[高級職業學校|高級職業學校]]」兩種。截至2010年，克國共有2,131所小學和713所學校提供各種[[中等教育|中等教育]]，在初級和中等教育上克國允許使用多種少數民族語言，包括[[捷克语|捷克语]]、[[匈牙利语|匈牙利语]]、意大利語、塞爾維亞語和德語<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|522}}。

截至2014年，克國有2060所初等和53所中等教育的{{link-en|藝術學校|Art school}}、75所供肢體傷殘兒童和青年、73所供成人就讀的特殊學校<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|518-519}}。2009至2010年間還引入了適用全國中等教育學生的[[畢業會考|畢業會考]]制度，考科包括三門必修科目（克羅地亞語、[[数学|数学]]和外語）和選修科目，為接受高等教育的先決條件<ref name="MZOS-Matura">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher = MZOS - Novosti
 | url = http://public.mzos.hr/Default.aspx?sec=2246
 | title = Državna matura
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160326060402/http://public.mzos.hr/Default.aspx?sec=2246
 | archivedate = 2016-03-26
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。

克羅地亞共有八所大學：[[萨格勒布大学|萨格勒布大学]]、{{link-en|斯普利特大學|University of Split}}、{{link-en|里耶卡大學|University of Rijeka}}、{{link-en|奧西耶克大學|University of Osijek}}、{{link-en|扎達爾大學|University of Zadar}}、{{link-en|杜布羅夫尼克大學|University of Dubrovnik}}、[[普拉大学|普拉大学]]和{{link-en|杜布羅夫尼克國際大學|Dubrovnik International University}}。
扎達爾大學是克羅地亞第一所大學，成立於1396年，而後營運至1807年由其他高等教育機關接收，直至2002年才再度以「扎達爾大學」為名重新建立<ref name="Zadar-Uni">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Sveučilište u Zadru
 | url = http://www.unizd.hr/Onama/tabid/55/Default.aspx
 | title = O nama
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160107073503/http://www.unizd.hr/Onama/tabid/55/Default.aspx
 | archivedate = 2016-01-07
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。萨格勒布大学成立於1669年，是東南歐最古老、持續營運至今的大學<ref name="Zagreb-Uni">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = University of Zagreb
 | url = http://www.unizg.hr/homepage/about-university/history/
 | title = University of Zagreb 1699–2005
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403012739/http://www.unizg.hr/homepage/about-university/history/
 | archivedate = 2016-04-03
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。截至2014年，克羅地亞共有133所高等教育學校，提供超過16萬名學生學習<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|523}}。

另外，2013年時共有253家企業、政府、教育與非營利組織為克羅地亞科研系統服務，投入經費約260億庫納、聘僱9,308名全職科研人員<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|535}}。目前克國最大的科學研究機構為萨格勒布的{{link-en|羅傑·博什科維奇研究院|Ruđer Bošković Institute}}<ref name="JL-IRB">{{hr}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = Jutarnji list
 | url = http://www.jutarnji.hr/ciklotron--spojevi-i-novi-katalizatori---to-je-institut-ruder-boskovic-dao-svijetu-/823851/
 | title = 60. rođendan Instituta Ruđer Bošković: Svijetu je dao ciklotron, spojeve i novi katalizator
 | date = 2010-06-09
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222206/http://www.jutarnji.hr/ciklotron--spojevi-i-novi-katalizatori---to-je-institut-ruder-boskovic-dao-svijetu-/823851/
 | archivedate = 2016-03-03
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。

===公共衛生===
[[File:KBC_Rebro_aerial.jpg|thumb]]
克羅地亞有一套完整的{{link-en|全民健康保險 (制度)|universal health care|全民健康保險}}系統，可追溯至1891年的匈牙利-克羅地亞議會法令，規定所有的工廠工人和工匠們都必須納入的一套強制保險制度<ref name="RSP-1891">{{hr}}{{cite journal|journal=Revija za socijalnu politiku|issn=1330-2965|author=Siniša Zrinščak|title=Socijalna politika u kontekstu korjenite društvene transformacije postkomunističkih zemalja|date=2003-02|volume=10|issue=2|url=http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=47595|accessdate=2016-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002358/http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=47595|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=yes}}</ref>{{rp|135-159}}。2011年時，醫療保健的支出僅佔私人醫療保險和公共支出的0.6％<ref name="Vjesnik-Zdravstvo">{{hr}}{{cite news |newspaper=Vjesnik |url=http://www.vjesnik.hr/Article.aspx?ID=B02A10F4-BFE5-4EC0-B0E5-BFCAFE8F2062 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68PYvmxY0?url=http://www.vjesnik.hr/Article.aspx?ID=B02A10F4-BFE5-4EC0-B0E5-BFCAFE8F2062 |title=Ulaskom u EU Hrvatska će imati najveću potrošnju za zdravstvo |author=Marijana Matković |date=2011-09-27 |accessdate=2011-10-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而醫療保健的總支出佔國內生產總值的7.9％<ref name="WB-Health">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = World Bank
 | url = http://www.worldbank.org/en/country/croatia/overview
 | title = Croatia Overview
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208140613/http://www.worldbank.org/en/country/croatia/overview
 | archivedate = 2015-12-08
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。根據2013年的世界衛生組織的資料，克羅地亞人預期壽命為[[各国人口预期寿命列表|男性75歲和女性81歲]]，每人平均衛生健康相關支出為1,517美金<ref name="WHO-Croatia-Stat">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = World Health Organization
 | title = Croatia
 | url = http://www.who.int/countries/hrv/en/
 | accessdate = 2016-07-12
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160429015506/http://www.who.int/countries/hrv/en/
 | archivedate = 2016-04-29
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。

克羅地亞國內有著數百個醫療機構，包括79座醫院和23,967個病床，醫治了超過74萬病例，聘僱了5,205名[[醫師|醫師]]，其中有3,929名[[專科醫師|專科醫師]]，總計共有41,271名醫療工作者。另外，2011年後，中央的[[緊急醫療服務|緊急醫療服務]]單位被撤除，由各縣相應機關提供其服務，2014年時共有92處縣級緊急醫療服務單位<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|565}}。截至2013年，克國人的主要死因為心血管疾病，約佔男性死因中的41.8％與女性的54.3％，第二大死因為惡性腫瘤，佔男性32.1％和女性23.6％<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|124}}。截至2014年，克國共有22名[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]患者，其中4人已死亡<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|569}}。

==文化==
{{Main|克羅地亞文化}}
===總論===
[[File:Necktie_knot.jpg|thumb]]是源自17世紀克羅地亞的一種服飾]]
克羅地亞的地理位置造就其涵蓋了四種文化的交融，包括東西兩方的[[拜占庭帝国|拜占庭帝国]]和[[西羅馬帝國|西羅馬帝國]]，以及[[中歐|中歐]]和{{link-en|地中海文化|Mediterranean culture}}<ref name="HTZ-History-Culture">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Croatian National Tourist Board
 | url = http://croatia.hr/en-GB/Discover-Croatia/Culture-and-History
 | title = Culture and History
 | accessdate = 2016-07-02
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111016185426/http://croatia.hr/en-GB/Discover-Croatia/Culture-and-History
 | archivedate = 2011-10-16
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。十九世紀盛行的「[[伊利里亞運動|伊利里亞運動]]」是克國文化發展史的重要時期，不僅解放了克羅地亞人的語言，還擴散到文化藝術等多種領域，多位重要的文化人士也跟著崛起<ref name="CRIS-Stančić">{{hr}}{{cite journal
 | journal = Cris: časopis Povijesnog društva Križevci
 | issn = 1332-2567
 | url = http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=80164
 | author = Nikša Stančić
 | title = Hrvatski narodni preporod – ciljevi i ostvarenja
 | volume = 10
 | issue = 1
 | date = 2009-02
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160703041059/http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=80164
 | archivedate = 2016-07-03
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>{{rp|6-17}}。
克國由{{link-en|文化部 (克羅埃西亞)|Ministry of Culture (Croatia)|文化部}}負責維護國家{{link-en|克羅埃西亞的文化和自然遺產|Natural and Cultural Heritage of Croatia|文化和自然遺產}}，並監督其發展，而更進一步支援文化事務則交由各地方政府推行<ref name="MKult-Djelokrug">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Ministarstvo kulture
 | url = http://www.min-kulture.hr/default.aspx?id=348
 | title = Djelokrug
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111124053511/http://www.min-kulture.hr/default.aspx?id=348
 | archivedate = 2011-11-24
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。克羅地亞共有{{link-en|克羅地亞世界遺產列表|World Heritage Sites in Croatia|7個景點}}被列入[[聯合國教育、科學及文化組織|聯合國教育、科學及文化組織]]的《[[世界遺產|世界遺產名錄]]》<ref name="UNESCO-WH">{{en}}{{cite web
 | url = http://www.worldheritagesite.org/countries/croatia.html
 | title = World Heritage Sites in Croatia
 | publisher = UNESCO
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110226031754/http://www.worldheritagesite.org/countries/croatia.html
 | archivedate = 2011-02-26
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>，並有高達10項[[人类非物质文化遗产代表作名录|非物质文化遗产]]，與[[西班牙|西班牙]]相同，超過其他所有歐洲國家<ref name="UNESCO-Masterpieces">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = UNESCO
 | url = http://www.unesco.org/culture/ich/index.php?lg=en&pg=00011&multinational=3&display1=countryIDs#tabs
 | title = Intangible Heritage Lists
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013010531/http://www.unesco.org/culture/ich/index.php?lg=en&pg=00011&multinational=3&display1=countryIDs#tabs
 | archivedate = 2012-10-13
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref>。克羅地亞還有一個風行全世界的文化特產——[[領帶|領帶]]，起初是克羅地亞人的男人在出征前由妻子或女朋友繫在脖子上的方巾，以示對他們的支持和鼓勵，而到了17世紀上半葉的「三十年戰爭」，克羅地亞作為法國盟友派出軍隊，脖子上有著獨特裝束的士兵們引起巴黎婦女們的注意，從而推廣到全世界，變成現在的領帶，也因此在[[德語|德語]]、[[法語|法語]]、[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]、[[意大利語|意大利語]]等歐洲語言中，「克羅地亞」一詞也有代指領帶之意<ref name="NYT-tie">{{en}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = The New York Times
 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1995/07/30/magazine/style-dressed-to-kill.html
 | title = STYLE; Dressed to Kill
 | author = Eric P. Nash
 | date = 1995-07-30
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121109043724/http://www.nytimes.com/1995/07/30/magazine/style-dressed-to-kill.html
 | archivedate = 2012-11-09
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref><ref name="Huzjan">{{hr}}{{cite journal
 |journal     = Povijesni prilozi
 |url         = http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=43829
 |publisher   = Hrčak Portal znanstvenih časopisa Republike Hrvatske
 |date        = 2008-07
 |volume      = 34
 |issue       = 34
 |author      = Vladimir Huzjan
 |title       = Pokušaj otkrivanja nastanka i razvoja kravate kao riječi i odjevnoga predmeta
 |issn        = 0351-9767
 |accessdate  = 2016-07-03
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817095741/http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=43829
 |archivedate = 2016-08-17
 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref>{{rp|103-120}}<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|32}}。

截至2014年，克羅地亞全國有93座專業劇院、24座專業兒童劇院和55座業餘劇院，每年有147萬人次前往觀看，年播放159部電影，票房共超過408萬人次。全國共有52個專業樂團、合唱團和唱詩班，每年吸引524,000人前往觀看<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|544-545}}。截至2012年，全國有181座博物館，約228萬人造訪<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|548}}。另外，截至2013年，克國共有1,781座圖書館，收藏2614萬冊書<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|550}}，在2014年時還有19座檔案館<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|551}}。2010年，克羅地亞全國共有超過7,300種書籍和冊子被印刷出版，連同包括2,678種雜誌和267種報紙<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|543}}。2014年時，全國有138個電台和26家電視台<ref name="統計2015"/>{{rp|543}}。

克羅地亞是一個[[性別平等|性別平等]]、高[[人类发展指数|人类发展指数]]的國家<ref name="UNDP-Croatia-HDI">{{en}}{{cite web
 | url = http://hdr.undp.org/en/media/HDR_2010_EN_Tables_reprint.pdf
 | title = Human Development Report 2010 Table 4 Gender Inequality Index
 | publisher = United Nations Development Programme
 | format = PDF
 | accessdate = 2016-07-03
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310235331/http://hdr.undp.org/en/media/hdr_2010_en_tables_reprint.pdf
 | archivedate = 2016-03-10
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>，在同性戀議題上，克國自2014年7月起承認同性伴侶的[[民事結合|民事結合]]，給予平等的繼承權、稅收減免和有限的領養權<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 | author = Scott Roberts
 | title = Croatia passes civil partnerships law
 | url = http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2014/07/15/croatia-passes-civil-partnerships-law/
 | publisher = PinkNews
 | date = 2014-07-15
 | accessdate = 2016-07-07
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160707023907/http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2014/07/15/croatia-passes-civil-partnerships-law/
 | archivedate = 2016-07-07
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>，然而根據[[2013年克羅地亞修憲公民投票|2013年的修憲公投]]結果，法理上的婚姻只能在「一男一女」的條件下成立<ref name="gay marriage reuters">{{en}}{{cite web
 | url = http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/12/01/uk-croatia-referendum-idUKBRE9B005V20131201
 | title = Croats set constitutional bar to same-sex marriage
 | author = Zoran Radosavljević
 | date = 2013-12-01
 | publisher = Reuters.com
 | accessdate = 2016-07-07
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140811200856/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/12/01/uk-croatia-referendum-idUKBRE9B005V20131201
 | archivedate = 2014-08-11
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>。

===文學藝術===

克羅地亞的建築藝術受到周遭國家的影響至深，北部與中部地區的建物反映了奧地利與匈牙利、沿海的達爾馬提亞以及伊斯特里亞則為威尼斯的風格<ref>{{en}}{{cite book|title=A short history of Yugoslavia from early times to 1966|publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|CUP Archive]]|isbn=978-0-521-09531-0|author1=Stephen Clissold|author2=Henry Clifford Darby|year=1968<!--|accessdate=2011-11-30-->}}</ref>{{rp|51-52}}。克國的建物特點為形式規劃整齊，各城鎮以文化英雄命名的大型廣場、公園、行人專用道皆為如此，如瓦拉日丁和卡爾洛瓦茨兩者即用採大規模的[[巴洛克建築|巴洛克風格]]來規劃整座城市<ref name="Varaždin-CTB-Baroque">{{en}}{{cite web
 | publisher = Varaždin Country Tourist Board
 | url = http://www.turizam-vzz.hr/en/posjetite/varazdin/
 | title = Varaždin – Baroque Capital of Croatia
 | accessdate = 2011-10-10
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100812064744/http://www.turizam-vzz.hr/en/posjetite/varazdin/
 | archivedate = 2010-08-12
 | deadurl = yes
 }}</ref><ref name="JL-Karlovac-Baroque">{{hr}}{{cite news
 | newspaper = Jutarnji list
 | url = http://www.jutarnji.hr/najljepsi-gradovi-sjeverne-hrvatske---karlovac--ozalj--ogulin/877654/
 | title = Najljepši gradovi Sjeverne Hrvatske – Karlovac, Ozalj, Ogulin
 | date = 2010-08-14
 | accessdate = 2011-10-10
 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160707170843/http://www.jutarnji.hr/arhiva/najljepsi-gradovi-sjeverne-hrvatske-karlovac-ozalj-ogulin/2121849/
 | archivedate = 2016-07-07
 | deadurl = no
 }}</ref>，反映出[[新艺术运动|新艺术运动]]充分影響了當代建築的風格<ref name="IPU-Art-Nouveau">{{hr}}{{cite journal 
 |journal=Radovi Instituta za povijest umjetnosti 
 |issn=0350–3437 
 |publisher=Institute of Art History (Croatia) 
 |format=PDF 
 |url=http://www.hart.hr/uploads/documents/354.pdf 
 |author=Darja Radović Mahečić 
 |title=Sekvenca secesije – arhitekt Lav Kalda 
 |year=2006 
 |volume=30 
 |accessdate=2016-07-08 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721100230/http://www.hart.hr/uploads/documents/354.pdf 
 |archivedate=2011-07-21 
 |deadurl=yes 
 }}</ref>{{rp|241-264}}。沿岸都市方面，克羅地亞一直受到意大利的影響，維持著羅馬式建築風格，直到後來威尼斯崛起和文藝復興的風潮才改變，當時的建築師中以{{link-en|乔治·达·塞贝尼科|Giorgio da Sebenico}}和{{link-en|尼科洛·迪·乔瓦尼·菲奥伦蒂诺|Niccolò Fiorentino}}兩人最具代表性，現今被列出「[[世界遺產|世界遺產]]」的希贝尼克[[圣雅各伯主教座堂_(希贝尼克)|圣雅各伯主教座堂]]即出自前者的設計。目前克羅地亞保存下來的最古老建築物是9世紀的教堂，最大和最具代表性的是[[聖多納圖斯教堂|聖多納圖斯教堂]]<ref name="MVPEI-Art">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher=Ministarstvo vanjskih i europskih poslova
 | url=http://www.mfa.hr/MVP.asp?pcpid=1467
 | title=CROATIAN ART HISTORY – OVERVIEW OF PREHISTORY
 | accessdate=2011-10-10
 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307231521/http://www.mfa.hr/MVP.asp?pcpid=1467
 | archivedate=2012-03-07
 | dead-url=yes
 }}</ref><ref name="TZZadar-Donat">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher=Zadar Tourist Board
 | url=http://www.tzzadar.hr/en/city-guide/historical-monuments/23-05-2007/church-of-saint-donat
 | title=Church of Saint Donat
 | accessdate=2011-10-10
 | archive-date=2014-03-24
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324042000/http://www.tzzadar.hr/en/city-guide/historical-monuments/23-05-2007/church-of-saint-donat
 | dead-url=yes
 }}</ref>。

除了建築外，克羅地亞的各種藝術也有著中世紀至今的悠久歷史，以雕塑來說，最著名的是萨格勒布的[[聖馬爾谷教堂_(札格瑞布)|聖馬爾科大教堂]]的南門，刻有哥德式的聖徒雕像，[[聖老楞佐主教座堂_(特羅吉爾)|聖老楞佐主教座堂]]也被認為是中世紀雕塑藝術的典範<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|290}}。後來克羅地亞的大部份地區都被捲入了與鄂圖曼土耳其的百年戰爭，未被捲入的沿海地區成了文藝復興的主要發展地，在鄂圖曼帝國的衰落後，克羅地亞地區的[[洛可可|洛可可]]與[[巴洛克艺术|巴洛克艺术]]才跟著出現。19世紀與20世紀，在如{{link-en|約瑟普·尤拉伊·史特羅斯梅爾|Josip Juraj Strossmayer}}這類的藝術喜好者的幫助下，克羅地亞的藝術家們有了繁榮的發展<ref name="Essehist-Strossmayer">{{hr}}{{cite journal
|journal=Essehist
|publisher=University of Osijek – Faculty of Philosophy
|issn=1847-6236
|date=2011-09
|volume=2
|url=http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=95675
|title=Josip Juraj Strossmayer – Rođeni Osječanin
|author=Pavao Nujić
|accessdate=2011-10-10
|archive-date=2019-12-13
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213020531/http://hrcak.srce.hr/index.php?show=clanak&id_clanak_jezik=95675
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>{{rp|70-73}}。在歷經二次大戰後，克羅地亞也跟著迎合當時的反法西斯、民族解放熱潮而有了大量相關題材的作品，其中{{link-hr|法尼亞·拉達烏什|Vanja Radauš}}為這一時期雕塑家的代表人物<ref name="列國志"/>{{rp|291}}。

[[克爾克島|克爾克島]]的「{{link-en|巴斯卡碑文|Baška tablet}}」是迄今為止被發現最古老的克羅地亞散文，以[[格拉哥里字母|格拉哥里字母]]撰寫，時間為西元1100年<ref name="KRK-Baška">{{hr}}{{cite web
 | publisher=Island of Krk Tourist Board
 | url=http://www.krk.hr/en/offer/attractions/the_baska_tablet
 | title=The Baška tablet
 | accessdate=2011-10-13
 | archive-date=2019-05-02
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502052935/http://www.krk.hr/en/offer/attractions/the_baska_tablet
 | dead-url=yes
 }}</ref>。克羅地亞文學在[[文藝復興|文藝復興]]時期蓬勃發展，其著名的文學家包括被尊為「克羅地亞文學之父」的詩人[[马尔科·马鲁利奇|马尔科·马鲁利奇]]、杜布羅夫尼克文藝復興文化代表的劇作家{{link-en|馬林·德爾日奇|Marin Držić}}、巴洛克詩人{{link-en|伊萬·貢杜里奇|Ivan Gundulić}}、[[伊利里亞運動|伊利里亞運動]]時期的詩人{{link-en|伊萬·馬祖拉尼奇|Ivan Mažuranić}}、小說家、劇作家兼詩人的{{link-en|奧古斯特·舍諾阿|August Šenoa}}、詩人兼作家的{{link-en|安頓·古斯塔夫·馬托什|Antun Gustav Matoš}}、詩人{{link-en|安頓·布朗克·希米奇|Antun Branko Šimić}}、[[表现主义|表现主义]]和[[现实主义|现实主义]]派作家[[米罗斯拉夫·克尔莱扎|米罗斯拉夫·克尔莱扎]]、詩人{{link-en|汀·烏耶維奇|Tin Ujević}}、小說家[[伊沃·安德里奇|伊沃·安德里奇]]常被認為是克羅地亞文學界中最出色的人物，他的《{{link-en|德里納河上的橋|The Bridge on the Drina}}》令其獲頒1961年的[[諾貝爾文學獎|諾貝爾文學獎]]<ref name="LZMK">{{hr}}{{cite web
 |publisher   = Miroslav Krleža Lexicographical Institute
 |url         = http://www.lzmk.hr/hr/vijesti-zavoda/iz-medija/524-hrvatska-knjizevnost-u-270000-redaka-vjesnik
 |date        = 2011-02-11
 |title       = Hrvatska književnost u 270.000 redaka
 |accessdate  = 2011-10-13
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20111217062534/http://www.lzmk.hr/hr/vijesti-zavoda/iz-medija/524-hrvatska-knjizevnost-u-270000-redaka-vjesnik
 |archivedate = 2011-12-17
}}</ref><ref name="NYT-Readerguide">{{hr}}{{cite news
 |url          = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F0CE7D91531F93BA25757C0A965958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all
 |title        = A Reader's Guide to the Balkans
